### List all available Projects [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [Projects Collection][]

### Create a Project [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "type": "Type of Project",
            "title": "Title of Project"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "id": 1,
                "title": "New project",
            }

